  "description": "<p><strong>We’re Brewing Something Big — Events & Marketing Reps Wanted!</strong><br /></p><p>You’re the kind that walks in and lights up the room.<br />You’ve got that espresso energy — confident, vibrant, and just the right amount of bold.<br /></p><p>💥 The Job:</p><ul><li>Represent big-name brands at exciting events</li><li>Engage people with your spark & charisma</li><li>Learn the ropes of sales, marketing, and leadership</li></ul><p>🔥 We Promise:</p><ul><li>No boring routines ☕</li><li>Just vibes, growth & travel ✈️</li><li>Training from zero to hero 💪</li></ul><p>Got that main-character glow? Then this gig might just be your caffeine kick.</p>",
